The paper discusses question answering models and their ability to learn incrementally, which falls under the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of language models (cs.IR) and the joint learning of multiple tasks (cs.NE).
